    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Repairs consisting of a localized cast of molten copper alloy to fill cavities or other casting defects. Cast-on repairs may fill a void in a sculpture or secure a separately formed patch or element to the cast.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
